{"tid":2422660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（中共送大禮）廣深磁能線懸浮廣州東站經南沙直插香港！","createTime":"2021-02-25T10:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T11:04:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"d113fd7dc4f80b1dbd024a7dba565735beffb23d","tid":2422660,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"備受關注的廣深磁懸浮建設線路有了最新最權威的消息。<br />\n<br />\n24日，在廣州市推進全球重要交通樞紐建設情況發佈會上，廣州市規劃和自然資源局公佈的規劃圖顯示，廣深高速磁懸浮預留線路將從廣州東站引出，一路南下經南沙，跨過珠江口後進入深圳寶安和前海，最後直入香港西九龍。<br />\n<br />\n這是廣深磁懸浮正式預留線路首次曝光，南沙也成了此條線路的最大受益者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0225%2F7c4dccdbj00qp1jsj004xc000u0016gg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0225%252F7c4dccdbj00qp1jsj004xc000u0016gg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=6b8c94f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，廣深磁懸浮時速約600公里，這也意味著，未來從廣州中心城區，只要不到10分鐘就可抵達南沙，而廣州到香港，亦在20分鐘之內抵達。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.bastillepost .com/hongkong/article/8023594</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8e14a1d76736700e34427f4707d15688472e13da","tid":2422660,"uid":82640,"like":124,"dislike":2,"score":122,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"無問題！<br />\n中共俾錢啦！<br />\n反正西九站都係中共境內！"},{"pid":"f32c42aeb002a56cdfbcd3ae90df2bbd6d2e289e","tid":2422660,"uid":388108,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:43:31.000Z","msg":"3穴中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779e9ae15534021a9b8c8f18202dcc09d905c8e9","tid":2422660,"uid":242537,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:44:05.000Z","msg"