35beffb23d","tid":2422660,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"備受關注的廣深磁懸浮建設線路有了最新最權威的消息。<br />\n<br />\n24日，在廣州市推進全球重要交通樞紐建設情況發佈會上，廣州市規劃和自然資源局公佈的規劃圖顯示，廣深高速磁懸浮預留線路將從廣州東站引出，一路南下經南沙，跨過珠江口後進入深圳寶安和前海，最後直入香港西九龍。<br />\n<br />\n這是廣深磁懸浮正式預留線路首次曝光，南沙也成了此條線路的最大受益者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0225%2F7c4dccdbj00qp1jsj004xc000u0016gg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0225%252F7c4dccdbj00qp1jsj004xc000u0016gg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=6b8c94f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，廣深磁懸浮時速約600公里，這也意味著，未來從廣州中心城區，只要不到10分鐘就可抵達南沙，而廣州到香港，亦在20分鐘之內抵達。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.bastillepost .com/hongkong/article/8023594</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFqFqyS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFqFqyS.gif&h=655ee49a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aefc8a1fa8a701e01e2d906bfafeaeb6b9ad3595","tid":2422660,"uid":135276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"又有基建，肥肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n準備定錢出埋大陸果份，營運頭果十幾年就比你地香港攪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3813ea76907b3e79ba3245b4e6b40ec9dd241114","tid":2422660,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"80億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br