/>\n<br />\n這是廣深磁懸浮正式預留線路首次曝光，南沙也成了此條線路的最大受益者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0225%2F7c4dccdbj00qp1jsj004xc000u0016gg.jpg&amp;thumbnail=750x2147483647&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=750x0&amp;quality=85&amp;type=jpg&amp;interlace=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnimg.ws.126.net%2F%3Furl%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fdingyue.ws.126.net%252F2021%252F0225%252F7c4dccdbj00qp1jsj004xc000u0016gg.jpg%26thumbnail%3D750x2147483647%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D750x0%26quality%3D85%26type%3Djpg%26interlace%3D1&h=6b8c94f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據悉，廣深磁懸浮時速約600公里，這也意味著，未來從廣州中心城區，只要不到10分鐘就可抵達南沙，而廣州到香港，亦在20分鐘之內抵達。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.bastillepost .com/hongkong/article/8023594</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"可以拆高鐵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214ee45dc82478f58756fcddd1bcd21db49c6494","tid":2422660,"uid":27946,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"去廣州東站點都有用過去廢物南站<br />\n港豬比支那槍拍閪住個頭無得唔起架啦<br />\n但西九膠鐵出條專線直入去粵西仲好<br />\n北京上海都係飛機算鳩數啦<br />\n好撚想睇經深圳d大巴撚執曬<br />\n到時等睇廣州返生而深圳收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2706f491328a65ab624247a00d52b12cf38684da","tid":2422660,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"條鳩鐵即刻變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c03c4746924ba8f237e9dd0a611e8c868ade9cd","tid":2422660,"uid":228205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35d91decde0de3363f5ae7551eca05f6cb2d6936","tid":2422660,"uid":106,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6a60b27eb871311ca08db6a597e7c4d1d7752d79","tid":2422660,"uid":288913,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"擺明唔受深圳玩<img src=\"/assets